Spend each Tuesday morn at 8

1241
01:12:17,110 --> 01:12:20,444
With Judaline

1242
01:12:21,185 --> 01:12:23,813
Don't forget you've got a date

1243
01:12:23,813 --> 01:12:27,480
With Judaline

1244
