asking silly questions...

1438
01:23:22,770 --> 01:23:25,540
...because you'd know yourself
what was going on.

1439
01:23:25,540 --> 01:23:27,741
Now, any further questions, Mr. Pringle?

1440
01:23:27,741 --> 01:23:31,445
